metadata.description:
Pepeshi's Diamonds are a revolutionary new digital technology built on the Bitcoin Ordinals protocol. 

Only those who own and burn Ethereum Coal can create a Pepeshi Diamond. Owning a Pepeshi Diamond makes you a true Bitcoin Diamond Hander, something no one can take away from you.

These diamonds are not just any ordinary digital tokens; they are securely recorded on the unalterable Bitcoin blockchain, and their token ID determines their unique positioning within the set.
metadata.name: Pepeshi's Diamonds (Ordinals) #1
